{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Banner_SwordFighting.png?t=1703263729\" /><br>Swordsman is a realistic sword-fighting game with challenging opponents and epic boss fights. Experience real combat that requires strategy against armored, physically simulated enemies that can parry, riposte, step, and dodge in this action-packed, award-winning game! Approach every fight like a real duel \u2014 parry enemies and strike them when they're weak!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/SS_Steam_Awards_2020-2021.png?t=1703263729\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Banner_Physics.png?t=1703263729\" /><br>Physically simulated weapons and realistic armor physics will challenge you in this visceral combat experience. Master the blade and become the ultimate Swordsman in VR!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/GIF_Physics.gif?t=1703263729\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Factions_Banner_160.png?t=1703263729\" /><br>To save humanity, you'll have to defeat armies from all over the world. Knights, Vikings, Mongols, Samurai, Pirates and more. Epic battles on ships in the Caribbean, duel to the death in the Gobi desert or clash with Hel, the goddess of the Underworld.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/GIF_Factions.gif?t=1703263729\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Weapons_Banner_160.png?t=1703263729\" /><br>Visit the Blacksmith to purchase weapons or take down powerful bosses to unlock their unique weapons and their special abilities. Gear up for increasingly difficult fights on your quest to find the J\u00f6tunn. Experience our released &quot;Advanced Weapon Handling&quot; update.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Screen_Weapons.jpg?t=1703263729\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/RPG_Banner_160.png?t=1703263729\" /><br>Weapons alone will not be enough to defeat the J\u00f6tunn and his armies. Visit the Skill Master to upgrade your stats and skills and the Armorer to equip yourself with better armor. Be strategic and build your ideal character build to suit your unique playstyle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Screen_SkillMaster.jpg?t=1703263729\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/extras/Features_Banner_160.png?t=1703263729\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Advanced combat mechanics with intelligent opponents that can engage in real sword-play<br></li><li> Seven different thematic combat environments<br></li><li> Dismemberment, armor physics, hand-to-hand combat and advanced weapon handling<br></li><li> Factions, including: Knights, Vikings, Mongols, Samurai, Pirates and eight different bosses<br></li><li> Horde: a zombie survival mode<br></li><li> Various weapon types<br></li><li> Player progression and RPG elements<br></li><li> Dozens of armors, weapons and shields (including powerful boss weapons)<br></li><li> Campaign, Arena and Event modes<br></li><li> Lots of stats and skills to upgrade for your ideal character build<br></li><li> Chronokinesis to slow time down (with a modifier to let you do it whenever you want)<br></li><li> Gameplay modifiers to change the core game in fun and exciting ways<br></li><li> Participate in real-life events for real-life prizes</li></ul><br><br>Click above and join us on Discord to chat with the developers, get the latest news on Swordsman, and participate in contests and giveaways. Eager to see you there!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Boy Scout","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/1184d3bdef226b99f5ce45933aaac153c142f05c.jpg"},{"name":"Extrovert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/9ba965e2174de5801b63cb7ede573e2c649ea394.jpg"},{"name":"Untouchable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/5f07dcba725565b3d4300050d115cd821050fdf9.jpg"},{"name":"Bullseye","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/260df920b2600ae4e42ecb86c799ccae72b0a3f4.jpg"},{"name":"Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/b75eafc4ede0128511258cf320944c38aa649f5f.jpg"},{"name":"Hellfire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/435ead042756237f72099353dbce5b456852f7f9.jpg"},{"name":"Barbarian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/66603d30fe6b5e727aa2fb15de3b9ca7ccfc363e.jpg"},{"name":"Madman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/fb750ff26cac2a3a0496880577ad9ad8c2a1a774.jpg"},{"name":"The Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/e7b846f09be7ebba8493fa7fd8b8a822b1d821f0.jpg"},{"name":"The Heavyweight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1206480/497a62f9f8cc69f6c79a5ef040de7436a58f5e78.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1703263729","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app